{% comment %}
  APEX — Checkout Section
  File: sections/apex-checkout.liquid

  WHAT THIS SECTION DOES:
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  Renders a full-page premium checkout experience that:
  1. Shows the selected plan (passed via URL param ?plan=operator|apex_class|free)
  2. Displays an order summary with the plan details
  3. Collects name + email + optional company
  4. Has a billing toggle (monthly / annual) with live price switching
  5. Connects to Shopify's native checkout via product variant IDs
  6. Falls back to a Stripe Checkout link if using Stripe directly
  7. Includes trust signals, guarantee badge, and animated effects

  INSTALL:
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  1. Edit Code → Sections → Add new section → name: apex-checkout
  2. Paste this file → Save
  3. Create a new Page in Shopify Admin, assign template or add this section
  4. Link your CTA buttons to /pages/checkout?plan=operator
     or /pages/checkout?plan=apex_class

  SHOPIFY PRODUCT SETUP:
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  Create two products in your Shopify store:
  - "APEX Operator" with two variants: Monthly ($12) and Annual ($84)
  - "APEX Apex Class" with two variants: Monthly ($29) and Annual ($204)
  Enter the variant IDs in the schema settings below.
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
{% endcomment %}

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>

